---
title: Chicken and Creamy Chive Sauce with Roasted Potatoes and Carrots
description: Creamy chive sauce envelops tender chicken with delicate onion flavour in this comforting weeknight wonder. Garlicky potato wedges and crisp carrots add the perfect balance to this decadent dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-dans-une-sauce-cremeuse-a-la-ciboulette-dd3d9610.jpg
